Syntax coloring and functions for YAML
=======================================
download yaml.vim from git repo
Save the file in ~/.vim/yaml.vim
Add the following line to your ~/.vimrc
 au BufNewFile,BufRead *.yaml,*.yml so ~/.vim/yaml.vim
